Chris Ramsey believes Tim Sherwood will keep Aston Villa in the Premier League . 
  Ramsey and Sherwood worked together at Tottenham and live within 10 minutes of each other . 
  QPR beat West Brom 4-1 on Saturday and face Villa on Tuesday night . 
  Ramsey says he would bet on Sherwood to keep Villa up if he was a betting man . 
 